00:37:20,004 --> 00:37:22,941
So I felt so happy. Really happy.

676
00:37:23,007 --> 00:37:25,110
I think our efforts paid off.

677
00:37:25,176 --> 00:37:26,177
So...

678
00:37:27,112 --> 00:37:28,713
