00:37:58,376 --> 00:37:59,744
the atmosphere was great

689
00:37:59,811 --> 00:38:01,746
as long as Shancai's dad was here.

690
00:38:01,813 --> 00:38:06,251
I think this was a unique experience.

691
00:38:06,885 --> 00:38:13,124
I think<i> Meteor Garden</i> lives up
