693
00:38:17,462 --> 00:38:18,963
As for me,

694
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:22,367
I'm so happy to cooperate
with these people to film this show.

695
00:38:22,433 --> 00:38:27,038
Because this show is loved
by many young people,

696
00:38:27,105 --> 00:38:30,175
