I'm more like your girl next door,

706
00:38:57,068 --> 00:38:59,070
but Jing is like your big sister.

707
00:38:59,137 --> 00:39:01,039
She's such a decent girl.

708
00:39:01,105 --> 00:39:03,241
So I think that was the challenge for me.

709
00:39:03,308 --> 00:39:07,045
Thank you, Chai, for the opportunity.

710
00:39:07,111 --> 00:39:10,615
Thank you, Director Tsai Yueh-Hsun,
for the guidance.

711
00:39:10,682 --> 00:39:12,984
I want to thank everyone and the staff.

712
00:39:13,051 --> 00:39:15,486
