but I think the staff had it the worst.

713
00:39:15,553 --> 00:39:18,957
Staff like the props team, lighting team,

714
00:39:19,023 --> 00:39:22,560
and the producer had to arrive before us.

715
00:39:22,627 --> 00:39:25,530
