and waited for us.

716
00:39:25,597 --> 00:39:27,465
I think they had it the worst.

717
00:39:27,532 --> 00:39:28,566
So...

718
00:39:30,068 --> 00:39:32,036
During the filming,

719
00:39:32,437 --> 00:39:36,841
