723
00:39:44,682 --> 00:39:46,918
if I can work with you again.

724
00:39:46,985 --> 00:39:48,753
Even if it happens again,
it won't be caused by me.

725
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:49,954
Right.

726
00:39:50,021 --> 00:39:55,159
I feel so happy to work with everyone
for these months.

727
00:39:55,226 --> 00:39:58,596
Maybe I will never meet another director
with such a good temper,

728
00:39:58,696 --> 00:40:01,466
nor will I meet such professional staff.

729
00:40:01,532 --> 00:40:03,234
One thing that impressed me was,

730
00:40:03,301 --> 00:40:04,936
